When creating solution guides use the following syntax to upload / share solution guides as well as upload new versions
:one: Initial Upload (Creates new guide)
curl -X POST https://solutions-master.replit.app/api/solution-guides/upload-curl \
  -H "X-Api-Key: sgk_lVKzPGWYeazXSqecUFsRMhpqLkKwrC6ZESgxZqlovNY" \
  -F "file=@/path/to/your-guide.html" \
  -F "title=Optional Custom Title" \
  -F "createShare=true" \
  -F "sharePassword=optional-password"
Response includes:
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Solution Guide uploaded successfully",
  "identifier": "62de5810-a1b2-c3d4-e5f6-1234567890ab",  // ← SAVE THIS!
  "guide": {
    "id": 25,
    "identifier": "62de5810-a1b2-c3d4-e5f6-1234567890ab",
    "title": "My Guide",
    "uploadedAt": "2025-11-05T21:30:00Z"
  }
}
:two: Update Version (Replaces existing guide)
Use the identifier from the initial upload response:
curl -X PUT https://solutions-master.replit.app/api/solution-guides/62de5810-a1b2-c3d4-e5f6-1234567890ab/upload-curl \
  -H "X-Api-Key: sgk_lVKzPGWYeazXSqecUFsRMhpqLkKwrC6ZESgxZqlovNY" \
  -F "file=@/path/to/updated-guide.html" \
  -F "title=Updated Title (optional)"
Response:
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Solution Guide updated successfully",
  "identifier": "62de5810-a1b2-c3d4-e5f6-1234567890ab",
  "guide": {
    "id": 25,
    "title": "Updated Title",
    "updatedAt": "2025-11-05T22:15:00Z"  // ← Timestamp shows it was updated
  }
}
:key: Key Parameters
For Upload (POST):
file (required) - The HTML file
title (optional) - Custom title, otherwise AI extracts it
createShare (optional) - Set to "true" to auto-generate share link
sharePassword (optional) - Password for share link
For Update (PUT):
file (required) - The new HTML file
title (optional) - New title, otherwise AI extracts it
identifier (in URL) - The unique identifier from initial upload
:white_check_mark: Features
:white_check_mark: Only latest version stored - Old content is replaced, not kept
:white_check_mark: Ownership enforced - You can only update your own guides
:white_check_mark: Auto-timestamps - updatedAt automatically tracks last update
:white_check_mark: Title flexibility - Provide custom title or let AI extract it
:white_check_mark: Same identifier - Keeps the same ID so share links still work
